### Analysis of the Main Target Image

**Structure on the Left:**
- **Layer 1 (Bottom):**
  - One yellow quarter cylinder.
  - One green rectangular block oriented vertically (flat side facing front).
- **Layer 2 (Middle):**
  - One red cylinder laying horizontally on top of the green block.

**Structure on the Right:**
- **Layer 1 (Bottom):**
  - Two red cylinders standing vertically.
- **Layer 2 (Middle):**
  - One horizontal yellow rectangular block connecting the two red cylinders.
- **Layer 3 (Top):**
  - One yellow quarter cylinder on top of the left-standing red cylinder.

- **Yellow Quarter Cylinder:** Index 14
- **Red Vertical Cylinder:** Index 10
- **Red Horizontal Cylinder:** Index 11
- **Yellow Horizontal Rectangular Block:** Index 6
